Name: netlink-packet-utils
URL: https://github.com/rust-netlink/netlink-packet-utils
Version: 0.5.2
Security Critical: yes

License File: LICENSE-MIT
  License: MIT

Description:
  This crate provides utilties for serialization/deserialization of NETLINK
  messages. It is used by Starnix to serve the NETLINK protocol.

  This crate forks upstream version 0.5.2. There are several divergences from
  upstream (See the git history for the complete list). At this point, there is
  no intention of re-merging with upstream.
